name: Snobz2
description: After a 3 week break from class I have completed my first project . Welcome to Snobz where one can explore coffee shops around the globe. This site was previously built by my friend on App Sheet , where I then took it upon myself to make a faster cleaner looking site. Most of the (vanilla) JavaScript is self taught from google, as well as working with leafletjs API. Later on (after returning to class and learning) I hope to use more common conventions and clean up up the code but until then....
